text: Sea bass is the name for different kinds of fish: *Barramundi (Lates calcarifer), or Asian Sea Bass *Black sea bass (Centropristis striata) *Chilean sea bass is a marketing name for the Patagonian toothfish *European seabass *Giant seabass *Potato cod *Suzuki (fish) *White seabass In addition, many fish are called bass
title: Sea bass
